  m_text: 'You have arrived in the desert, cuffed to a table.


    You see a tram
    hurdling towards a group of 5 individuals (pictures on the table). You must choose
    one to save them or risk your life:


    1.Press the button to save yourself,
    killing them.

    2. Don''t press the button to save them, killing yourself.


    Your
    decision is final once you do or don''t press the button.'
